Merchant Banking Partners II for $685 million. Biogums are used
mainly to improve the texture and processing of foods. Monsanto's
main biogums operations are in San Diego; Chicago; Okmulgee, Okla.;
and Knowsley, U.K. Meanwhile, shareholders for both Monsanto and
Pharmacia &AMP; Upjohn Inc. will hold special meetings March 23 to vote
on the proposed merger of the two companies.
</P>
